last_episode_to_air.name: Eight Flags Over the Nursery
last_episode_to_air.overview: When it will take five years to build the real amusement park the babies build their own - Babyland!

name: Muppet Babies
overview: The Muppet Babies (Kermit, Piggy, Gonzo, Fozzy and company) live in a large nursery watched over by Nanny. The babies have active imaginations, and often embark upon adventures into imaginary worlds.

episodes.name: Noisy Neighbors
episodes.overview: The Kids spend all day Trying to keep animal quiet so they don't disturb their next door neighbor officer caruthers.

episodes.name: Who's Afraid of The Big, Bad Dark?
episodes.overview: Bunsen hasn't been getting sleep lately each night beeker is waking up screaming saying that the monster attacked him in his sleep the kids realize that beeker is afraid of the ark and try to help him overcome his fears.

episodes.name: Dental Hijinks
episodes.overview: Foozie's tooth becomes loose and he worries about going to the dentist, and what the dentist will do to him.

episodes.name: Raiders of the Lost Muppet
episodes.overview: During a game of hide and seek, Animal gets lost. They search the nursery up and down. Until they eventually find out that Animal was with Nanny.

episodes.name: Scooter's Hidden Talent
episodes.overview: All of the babies are showing their talents, but Scooter can't seem to find his. By some inspiration, he learns his talent is being computer smart.

episodes.name: The Case of the Missing Chicken
episodes.overview: Gonzo panics when he can't find his stuff baby chicken camella.

episodes.name: Eight Take-Away One Equals Panic
episodes.overview: A Misunderstanding leads the kids to belive that Nanny is going to give one of them away.

episodes.name: What Do You Want To Be When You Grow Up?
episodes.overview: All the Muppet Babies except for Kermit know what jobs they want to have when they grow up. The babies show Kermit different jobs he can be, and he finally chooses to be a cab driver.

episodes.name: Close Encounters of the Frog Kind
episodes.overview: Kermit and the other Muppet Babies get to meet his little nephew, Robin, the tadpole. But since he is too small, they must find him after he esapes from his bowl.

episodes.name: Gonzo's Video Show
episodes.overview: Borrowing Nanny's camcorder, The Muppet Babies make their own movies including a ""Star Wars"" parody.

episodes.name: Fun Park Fantasies
episodes.overview: Instead of waiting a week to visit the fun park, the babies make their own park right in the nursery!

episodes.name: From a Galaxy Far, Far Away
episodes.overview: When an alien (really an escaped Koala) ends up in the Nursery, the kids build a rocketship out of their toys so they can take it back home.

episodes.name: Good, Clean Fun
episodes.overview: The babies accidently brake a lamp and try to compensate by preparing lunch, but they just ending up making up making a bigger mess, especially Animal.

episodes.name: Once Upon an Egg Timer
episodes.overview: The babies use an egg timer and a story to help Rowlf get his voice back.

episodes.name: Piggy's Hyper-Activity Book
episodes.overview: When all the babies have nothing to do, Piggy takes out her activity book to play with.

episodes.name: Fozzie's Last laugh
episodes.overview: Fozzie decides he doesn't want to be a comedian anymore when Piggy hurts his feelings.

episodes.name: The Great Cookie Robbery
episodes.overview: Gonzo secretly and selfishly keeps cookies to himself letting the other Muppet Babies suffer from hunger until they meet an imaginary cookie-hungry bandit, One-Eyed Jake.

episodes.name: Out-Of-This-World History
episodes.overview: The babies hear about the timeline of history.

episodes.name: Snow White and the Seven Muppets
episodes.overview: Bunson and Beaker come over, and the babies play Snow White. But Skeeter and Piggy argue over who is to play Snow White.

episodes.name: I Want My Muppet TV!
episodes.overview: After their real TV set goes bad, missing their favorite show. The Muppet Babies use a pretend TV set and make their own shows.

episodes.name: Musical Muppets
episodes.overview: Each Muppet Baby performs and records his or her own song for a song-writing contest and at the end, all their songs are played together as one.

episodes.name: Who's Who at the Zoo?
episodes.overview: The babies must convince Rolf that the zoo is not a prison for animals.

episodes.name: The Great Muppet Cartoon Show
episodes.overview: The Muppet Babies create their own cartoons.

episodes.name: The Muppet Museum of Art
episodes.overview: The Muppet Babies are about to go to the art museum when Skeeter gets hurt by one of Piggy's pink skates.  Before everyone could notice the skate, Piggy replaces her skate with Gonzo's in the scene of the accident so he could take the blame.  Since they can't go to the art museum now, the muppets decide to bring the art museum to the nursery by creating their own works of art.  Gonzo paints portraits of Piggy, but her roller skate mysteriously appears in Gonzo's paintings.   Freaked out by this, Piggy attempts to keep Gonzo's paintings out of sight.  The muppets then show their artwork to Nanny and an injured Skeeter.  When Gonzo shows to everyone a beautiful picture of Piggy, Piggy finally confesses to framing Gonzo and apologizes.

episodes.name: By the Book
episodes.overview: The kids are having a fun time playing boat races but when piggy cheats the fun turns into a disaster piggy claims that the rules were changed nanny tells them how rules should be agreed on and not be changed with out consulting everyone at first.

episodes.name: When You Wish Upon a Muppet
episodes.overview: The Muppet Babies play a wishing game where they each imagine their greatest wishes coming true.

episodes.name: Pigerella
episodes.overview: The twins decide to get some snacks from the kitchen but Piggy warns them of the consinquences for getting snacks without Nannny's permision they ignore her warning but when piggy tries to sneak the snacks back in the kitchen Nanny accuses her of stealing from the fridge and makes her clean up the mess.

episodes.name: The Best Friend I Never Had
episodes.overview: The Muppet Babies all want to have a perfect friend but find out that they are each not what they expect.

episodes.name: The Weirdo Zone
episodes.overview: Gonzo shows the other babies what its like to be a ""weirdo"" like him.

episodes.name: Muppets in Toyland
episodes.overview: Scooter gets an all new Transco JoBot, and all of the Muppets want one but Nanny gives them her old toys instead.

episodes.name: The Muppet Broadcasting Company
episodes.overview: When Nanny's TV breaks, and she complains that she can't watch the news, the Babies create their own news channel, ""MBC"". Each Muppet creates his/her own show, including Kermit and Fozzie in a newscast, and Piggy in her own soap opera.

episodes.name: Kermit Goes to Washington
episodes.overview: The babies have an election for president of the nursery, and Kermit wins.

episodes.name: Fozzie's Family Tree
episodes.overview: All of the babies find interesting relatives in their family tree, but Fozzie can't find his family tree. So he does not know anything about his family. Kermit and Fozzie search for some of Fozzie's relatives.

episodes.name: The Daily Muppet
episodes.overview: After Nanny's newspaper is ruined, the baies make their own paper of news for her.

episodes.name: Scooter's Uncommon Cold
episodes.overview: The babies travel inside Scooter to heal him of a cold.

episodes.name: Treasure Attic
episodes.overview: The babies explore the attic and find old stuff, that they never knew they had before.

episodes.name: Around the Nursery in 80 Days
episodes.overview: After the Muppet Babies hear that Nanny is going on an ""around the world"" trip and are worried that they will not have a good sitter to look after them. They try to have her trip be in the nursery until they find out that their stand-in nursemaid will be her sister, Aunt Fanny.

episodes.name: Fine Feathered Enemies
episodes.overview: The Muppet Babies befriend a talking parrot named Polly who causes them to misunderstand each other and quarrel with each other because of his loudmouthing.

episodes.name: Muppet Goose
episodes.overview: Nanny tries to get the Babies to go to sleep by telling Nursery Rhymes.

episodes.name: Bad Luck Bear
episodes.overview: After Fozzie breaks a mirror, Piggy tells him he will have bad luck for the next 7 years.

episodes.name: Of Mice and Muppets
episodes.overview: The kids are taking care of Caruther's pet mouse pewee while he is on vacation its rowlf's turn to put peewee back in his cage but he accidently leaves the door open and pewee escapes the kids go on a all night search for pewee before Nanny finds out.

episodes.name: Back to the Nursery
episodes.overview: When everyone is looking at Nanny's old photo album, Fozzie accidently spills cofee on an old picture of Nanny servng at a drive-through. The babies travel back in time, in a ""Back To The Future"" parody to re-take the picture of Nanny.

episodes.name: Muppetland
episodes.overview: The babies make they're own themepark, and each babie makes there own attraction.

episodes.name: Water Babies
episodes.overview: Nanny got an aqurarium for the muppets to look at.  Skeeter thought that looking for treasure is much fun than looking at the fishes.

episodes.name: The Incredible Shrinking Weirdo
episodes.overview: Gonzo thinks that he is shrinking when his basketball jersey is too big for him, but in reality He was wearing fozzie's jersey.

episodes.name: Where No Muppet Has Gone Before
episodes.overview: Bunsen and Beaker come over, and the babies learn about different things in outer space.

episodes.name: Journey to the Center of the Nursery
episodes.overview: After Fozzie's skate key falls down the air vent the kids go looking for it. The kids use the closet as an elevator. At each level they go down they find stranger and stranger things. The reason it's so important that Fozzie find his skate key is because he's still wearing his skates! He can't get them off! Throughout the episode Fozzie goes wheeling and sliding all over the place!

episodes.name: This Little Piggy Went to Hollywood
episodes.overview: Piggy tells the babies about how she wil become a movie star like Shirley Temple.

episodes.name: My Muppet Valentine
episodes.overview: Rowlf is bummed out about not getting a Valentine cookie from Nanny when the others did so the rest of the Muppet Babies try to cheer him up.  Rowlf dedicates a Valentine song to his friends and Nanny gives him his cookie, saying that she forgot to put it with the other cookies.

episodes.name: Invasion of the Muppet Snackers
episodes.overview: The babies smell Nanny's cooking, and itsmells really bad. They imagine how it will taste, and what it will look like. When dinner is served, they find out that the awful smell was wallpaper paste, that Nanny was using to re-decorate the bathrom with.

episodes.name: Twinkle Toe Muppets
episodes.overview: The babies try different types of dancing, but Scooter doesn't know which type is bes for him.

episodes.name: Weirdo for the Prosecution
episodes.overview: Gonzo is accused of breaking the cookie jar and stealing cookies, so the babies hold a trial to give him a chance to defend himself. (Boy, is he in trouble...)

episodes.name: Muppet Island
episodes.overview: A bunch of peanut butter and jelly gets spilled outside the Nursery door so the kids have to stay inside until Nanny can get it cleaned up. So they make their own island.

episodes.name: The Frog Who Knew Too Much
episodes.overview: Nanny has a big surprise for the kids Kermit is the first one to see it but the trouble is not telling the kids what it is.

episodes.name: Beach Blanket Babies
episodes.overview: Fozzie, who has never swum before, learns to swim. But it is very hard at first.

episodes.name: Old MacKermit Had a Farm
episodes.overview: The babies try to figure out where bluberry muffins come from.

episodes.name: Adventures in Muppet-Sitting
episodes.overview: The babies learn how hard it is to babysit when they have to look after Animal and Robin, Kermit's nephew.

episodes.name: The House That Muppets Built
episodes.overview: The babies accidently break Piggy's dollhouse, and then make one of their own for her.

episodes.name: Masquerading Muppets
episodes.overview: The baies are getting set to go to a costume party, so eac of them decide what to wear.

episodes.name: Nanny's Day Off
episodes.overview: The babies give Nanny a day off, and do all the work around the house so she doesn't have to.

episodes.name: Muppets Not Included
episodes.overview: The babies find a tea strainer of Nanny's, and do not know what it is. Each babie thinks of a different use for it.

episodes.name: Beauty and the Schnoz
episodes.overview: Piggy learns that ""beauty is in the eye of the beholder"", when she makes fun of Gonzo and it hurts his feelings.

episodes.name: The Pig Who Would Be Queen
episodes.overview: The babies bulid Nanny a ""picture box"" with a fairy tale scene, and each babie pretends to be a character.

episodes.name: Is There a Muppet in the House?
episodes.overview: Rowlf hadn't disapeared - he'd just watched a scary movie the night before and had gone to see Nanny. The secret passage was actually an old dumbwaiter which Animal found and had been using to move between the attic, kichen and basement.

episodes.name: Slipping Beauty
episodes.overview: Piggy gets the chicken pox, and tells the babies the story of Sleeping Beauty, through walkie-talkie.

episodes.name: Muppet Baby Boom
episodes.overview: All the babies look foward to seeing Mrs. Mitchell's baby, which ends up being a kitten.

episodes.name: Scooter By Any Other Name
episodes.overview: Scooter's tired of being a nerd, so Gonzo convinces him to reinvent himself; first as a jet fighter pilot, then as a stand-up comic, then as a rock star, and finally as a superhero.

episodes.name: He's a Wonderful Frog
episodes.overview: The Babies think Kermit is moving away, so stage a ""This is Your Life"" spoof to try and convince him to stay.

episodes.name: Elm Street Babies
episodes.overview: The babies describe their weird dreams to each other.

episodes.name: Plan 8 from Outer Space
episodes.overview: The babies see a news bulletin about disapearing nannies. Gonzo says that aliens have been nannynapping them because they use green stripped socks to power their spaceships (and only nannies wear green stripped socks).

episodes.name: Junkland Muppets
episodes.overview: The babies make things out of old junk, while Fozzie searches for his lost Teddy.

episodes.name: The Air Conditioner at the End of the Galaxy
episodes.overview: When the air-conditioner breaks down, Scooter and Piggy travel to find a place that is more cool.

episodes.name: Bug-Busting Babies
episodes.overview: The babies hunt for the bug in Scooter's computer in a parody of Ghostbusters.

episodes.name: This Old Nursery
episodes.overview: The babies find an old time capsule in the nursery walls.

episodes.name: And Now a Word From Our Muppets
episodes.overview: The babies make up adds for Nanny's garage sale.

episodes.name: Six to Eight Weeks
episodes.overview: The babies cant wait six to eight weeks for their playhouse to come.

episodes.name: The Green Ranger
episodes.overview: When Kermit's favorite cowboy show ""The Range Rider"" gets cancelled, he contemplates trying to fill in the Range Rider's shoes (as ""The Green Ranger""). But he thinks his friends might have the wrong idea, and it takes more than fame and merchandising to be a real hero.

episodes.name: Not Necessarily the Muppets
episodes.overview: The Babies discover the importance of why grown-ups watch the news, and with the nursery news, they find all their favorite toys.

episodes.name: Comic Capers
episodes.overview: The Muppet Babies look at comic books and comic strips and imagine themselves as the characters in them.

episodes.name: Faster Than a Speeding Weirdo
episodes.overview:
Gonzo attempts to break the sound berrier while riding on a vaccum cleaner. He brings his trusty sidekick, Camilla along for a ride. However, misfortune strikes, and Camilla gets hurt, and Gonzo is unsure she'll make it. Nanny has to perform ""emergency surgery"" on Camilla, but in the end, she's alright.

Gonzo sings the song ""Camilla"" to the babies, to show how upset he is about the thought of losing Camilla.

episodes.name: Skeeter and the Wolf
episodes.overview: Nanny read the muppets a story about Peter and the wolf.

episodes.name: Romancing the Weirdo
episodes.overview: Gonzo finds an old typewriter, and decides to write a detective novel (with himself as the hero, Philip Samuel Marlowe Spade, and Piggy as the heroine). Can his friends help him when he gets writer's block?

episodes.name: The New Adventures of Kermo Polo
episodes.overview: The babies pretend to be famous explorer's from different periods of time.

episodes.name: Goosetown Babies
episodes.overview: The babies read their favorite Mother Goose book, and are transported to Goosetown, when they realize that the town just isn't the same. So, taking the matters into their own hands, they visit Mother Goose, who believes that children don't like her tales anymore, and the residents of Goosetown have all stopped taking care of themselves. When the babies go around town patching things up, Mother Goose realizes that kids will always love her books, and everybody lives happily ever after.

episodes.name: It's Only Pretendo
episodes.overview: Piggy and Gonzo get so caught up in beating each other at ""Legend of Emelda: Quest for the Golden Key"", that they almost forget it's just a game, and the main goal should really be having fun.

episodes.name: Quoth the Weirdo
episodes.overview: The Muppet Babies celebrate the beauty that is poetry by talking about their favorite poems.

episodes.name: Operators are Standing By
episodes.overview: The babies wonder who could have been on the phone after Animal hangs up the phone.

episodes.name: Babes in Troyland
episodes.overview: The babies learn about different greek myths.

episodes.name: Puss 'n Boots 'n Babies
episodes.overview: The babies get exited about a kitty in the nursery.

episodes.name: Muppets of Invention
episodes.overview: Uncle Statler and Uncle Waldorf come to visit, and the babies make inventions of their own.

episodes.name: A Punch Line to the Tummy
episodes.overview: Fozzie's trying to be a real stand-up comedian, but Gonzo's attempts at getting ""feedback"" from his audience (the other Muppet Babies) make Fozzie think his friends don't like him anymore.

episodes.name: Muppet Babies: The Next Generation
episodes.overview: The babies parody The Jetsons, Star Trek, Bill & Ted, and Indiana Jones. Kermit pretends to be George Jetson, and tries to get Rolf to take a bath.

episodes.name: Buckskin Babies
episodes.overview: The babies pretend to be heroes from the old west.

episodes.name: Sing a Song of Superheroes
episodes.overview: The babies put on their own ""superhero opera"" while Nanny tries to watch the ""Phantom of the Opera""

episodes.name: Gonzee's Playhouse Channel
episodes.overview: Gonzo does his own conduit of tv.

episodes.name: Kermit Pan
episodes.overview: The Muppet Babies version of Peter Pan with Kermit as Peter Pan, Skeeter as Wendy and Piggy as Tinkerbell.

episodes.name: Whose Tale is it, Anyway?
episodes.overview: The babies tell their own tales to each other.

episodes.name: ...At The Movies
episodes.overview: The babies joke about the movies.

episodes.name: In Search of Bronze Beatle
episodes.overview: The babies search for the bronze beatle that they hear about.

episodes.name: Transcontinental Whoo-Whoo
episodes.overview: Statler and Waldorf join the kids in reenacting the construction of the Transcontinental Railroad.

episodes.name: Get Me to the Perch on Time
episodes.overview: After a messenger pigeon gets hurt outside the nursery window, the Babies help her by deliverying her messages around the world.

episodes.name: Beraly Alone Babies
episodes.overview: The Nanny leave to go to the market and she leaves the alone babies.

episodes.name: Remote Controlled Cornballs
episodes.overview: The babies joke about remote conrols.

episodes.name: Nice to Have Gnome You
episodes.overview: The Babies help Piggy find her book of ""Alice In Wonderland"" before the Book-Mobile arrives to pick-up the books. When Miss Piggy thinks she has lost it the rest of the gang helps her to make a new book with just pictures; drawn by themselves. The kids then learn that Nanny acutally had the book!

episodes.name: Happy Birthday Uncle Piggy
episodes.overview: Uncle Statler and Uncle Waldorf have an aniversary.

episodes.name: Hats, Hats, Hats
episodes.overview: The Babies have an adventure with the many different hats that Uncles Statler and Waldorf bring them.

episodes.name: Eight Flags Over the Nursery
episodes.overview: When it will take five years to build the real amusement park the babies build their own - Babyland!
